{"tid":1279571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講連登終於進駐Twitter","createTime":"2019-07-02T16:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:50:33.000Z","uid":267059,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19b89204c1dbb7b6b4bae67e884ef677cdd0d6ef","tid":1279571,"uid":267059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"撚咗幾年 Twitter 今日見到呢個消息太感動了 <br />\n<br />\n以下分享 Twitter 常用語 <br />\n輕鬆得嚟又會感覺入鄉地道一啲 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎有上開嘅人嚟交流下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遇到圖中留言我哋會講: <br />\n<br />\n&quot;so what about it?&quot; (你吹咩) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2T1oMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2T1oMP.png&h=a8c43fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Now say that without crying&quot; (類似 你唔葡萄得咁多㗎啦(收皮啦))  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ids3Og.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ids3Og.png&h=1ec6170e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;MY LUNGS JSJSJSJJ&quot; (笑到甩肺) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BQrzWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BQrzWf.png&h=a7c43e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n另外想要主流外國關注要留意唔好 racist &amp; sexist , 基本嘢就係唔用 n word (n*gg*) <br />\nc*ic* 同 c*nt. <br />\n<br />\ns worded = suspend <br />\n<br />\n冇 verified (tick) 嘅 account 用得多 fuck , kill , nword 暴力粗俗字眼好易比人 report 到封 account (suspend) 所以打 fuck 用 fcuk 係比較安全。<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n如果想 keep 外國關注最好推到上 worldwide trend <br />\n要消息散得快要善用 hashtag <br />\n<br />\n要做到咁你要喺唔同國家地區都有一定數量嘅 Tweet <br />\n唔只要 RT 要新嘅 original tweet (啫係你自己打同新 po 嘅) <br />\n<br />\n*但唔好將對我方不利消息同 tag 一齊用 <br />\n<br />\n不過已有嘅 #antiELAB 已經冇可能 trend到。 因為用咗一排 , 要 trend 係最好係要短時間谷到一個*新*嘅 tag 上過萬。有講法係最好只用一個 tag , 除非你係 ARMY , 佢哋撚 Twitter 無人能敵。<br />\n<br />\n祝閣下 Twitter 愉快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4580bae547b019de007b9e888d9eb2c775d8f145","tid":1279571,"uid":188969,"like":0,"d